Instructions:

You have one register which is initialized at 0.

█	Darkness, increments/decrements depending on mode
▄	Decrement switch
▀	Increment switch
─	Toggles ascii output on and off, default is off
■	Output
Turns:
╬ turn right if the register is non-zero, turn left if the register is zero
┼ turn right if the register is non-zero, turn left if the register is zero and also resets the register after the turn
<space> Terminate

You start heading east